com.github.jmkgreen.morphia
Interface AdvancedDatastore

All Superinterfaces:
Datastore
All Known Implementing Classes:
DatastoreImpl
public interface AdvancedDatastore
extends Datastore

This interface exposes advanced Datastore features, like interacting with DBObject and low-level options.

  • Implements matching methods from the Datastore interface but with a specified kind (collection name), or raw types (DBObject).

Author:
ScottHernandez
